thread.title_full: LymphedemaProducts.com reviewed by David W. Lutz

author: David W. Lutz
title: David W. Lutz
text: I was impressed by the amount of compression wrap I got for the money. The material is a little thin, but stretches nicely and compresses like it should. It's kind of tight on my legs, but that's just something on my part. I wasn't sure the exact size to get, but it came pretty close. It's still usable.
